{"componentChunkName":"component---node-modules-antv-gatsby-theme-antv-0-10-39-antv-gatsby-theme-antv-site-templates-document-tsx","path":"/zh/docs/specification/components/graphic","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"AntV","githubUrl":"https://github.com/antvis","docs":[{"slug":"specification/principles","title":{"zh":"设计原则","en":"Design Principles"},"order":0},{"slug":"specification/components","title":{"zh":"图表组件设计指引","en":"Design for Components of Charts"},"order":1}]},"pathPrefix":""},"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h2 id=\"定义\"><a href=\"#%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89\" aria-label=\"定义 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>定义</h2>\n<p>图形是统计图表的视觉通道在形状上映射的视觉展现，是图表的主体部分，其他图表组件的目的是帮助读者更好地理解数据在图形上的映射关系。</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"何时使用\"><a href=\"#%E4%BD%95%E6%97%B6%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8\" aria-label=\"何时使用 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>何时使用</h2>\n<p>图形可以通过视觉特征更快地被读者感知和接受。从认知学的角度，人眼在对图形的获取效率远高于对抽象意符的理解。所以图形是数据可视化的必备元素，承载着数据背后蕴含的信息。</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"类型\"><a href=\"#%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B\" aria-label=\"类型 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>类型</h2>\n<p>按照基础图表类型，图形可分为：折线，面积，散点，气泡，饼/环，柱形，条形。<br /><img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_f8c6a0/afts/img/A*RdOVQ5Sv3UIAAAAAAAAAAABkARQnAQ' width=750/></p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"样式\"><a href=\"#%E6%A0%B7%E5%BC%8F\" aria-label=\"样式 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>样式</h2>\n<p>二维空间内的统计图表图形属性遵循计算机视觉元素构成，有 填充，描边，阴影等样式。</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"用法建议\"><a href=\"#%E7%94%A8%E6%B3%95%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%AE\" aria-label=\"用法建议 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>用法建议</h2>\n<h4 id=\"图形比例\"><a href=\"#%E5%9B%BE%E5%BD%A2%E6%AF%94%E4%BE%8B\" aria-label=\"图形比例 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>图形比例</h4>\n<p>以柱形图为例，柱子比例和两边间距的比例为 1：2：1，柱子宽度为总宽度的 60%。</p>\n<h4 id=\"填充样式\"><a href=\"#%E5%A1%AB%E5%85%85%E6%A0%B7%E5%BC%8F\" aria-label=\"填充样式 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>填充样式</h4>\n<p>根据图形元素在实际图表中的面积占比，我们定义了相应的填充样式。图形占比越大的图表，对应填充的透明度越高。如，在柱/条形图中，图形的填充比例为 95%；在面积图中，图形的填充比例为 25%。<img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/zos/basement_prod/8fda1e44-7562-445a-9539-87044e1d02ba.svg' width=339/><img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/zos/basement_prod/a86e85af-1893-4fe3-bc5c-74784ef7801a.svg' width=341/></p>\n<p>持续更新中，敬请期待…</p>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/zh/docs/specification/components/graphic/#%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89\">定义</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/zh/docs/specification/components/graphic/#%E4%BD%95%E6%97%B6%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8\">何时使用</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/zh/docs/specification/components/graphic/#%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B\">类型</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/zh/docs/specification/components/graphic/#%E6%A0%B7%E5%BC%8F\">样式</a></li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/zh/docs/specification/components/graphic/#%E7%94%A8%E6%B3%95%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%AE\">用法建议</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/zh/docs/specification/components/graphic/#%E5%9B%BE%E5%BD%A2%E6%AF%94%E4%BE%8B\">图形比例</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/zh/docs/specification/components/graphic/#%E5%A1%AB%E5%85%85%E6%A0%B7%E5%BC%8F\">填充样式</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","fields":{"slug":"/zh/docs/specification/components/graphic","readingTime":{"text":"1 min read","time":11100}},"frontmatter":{"title":"图形设计指引"},"parent":{"relativePath":"specification/components/graphic.zh.md"}},"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/en/docs/specification/principles/basic"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Principles","order":0}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/zh/docs/specification/principles/basic"},"frontmatter":{"title":"设计原则","order":0}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/en/docs/specification/principles/visual"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Visual","order":1}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/zh/docs/specification/principles/visual"},"frontmatter":{"title":"视觉","order":1}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/en/docs/specification/principles/interact"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Interact","order":2}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/zh/docs/specification/principles/interact"},"frontmatter":{"title":"交互","order":2}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/en/docs/specification/components/titlenotes"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Title and Notes","order":3}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/zh/docs/specification/components/titlenotes"},"frontmatter":{"title":"标题与注释","order":3}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/en/docs/specification/principles/mobile"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Mobile","order":3}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/zh/docs/specification/principles/mobile"},"frontmatter":{"title":"移动","order":3}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/en/docs/specification/components/axis"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Axis","order":4}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/zh/docs/specification/components/axis"},"frontmatter":{"title":"轴","order":4}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/en/docs/specification/components/legend"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Legend","order":5}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/zh/docs/specification/components/legend"},"frontmatter":{"title":"图例","order":5}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/en/docs/specification/components/label"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Label","order":6}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/zh/docs/specification/components/label"},"frontmatter":{"title":"标签","order":6}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/en/docs/specification/components/graphic"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Tooltip","order":7}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/zh/docs/specification/components/tooltip"},"frontmatter":{"title":"提示信息","order":7}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/en/docs/specification/components/tooltip"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Tooltip","order":7}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/zh/docs/specification/components/graphic"},"frontmatter":{"title":"图形设计指引","order":8}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/en/docs/specification/resources"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Resource Download","order":10}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/zh/docs/specification/resources"},"frontmatter":{"title":"资源下载","order":10}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/en/docs/specification/reference"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Classical Literature","order":11}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/zh/docs/specification/reference"},"frontmatter":{"title":"经典文献","order":11}}}]}},"pageContext":{"prev":{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/zh/docs/specification/components/tooltip"},"frontmatter":{"title":"提示信息","order":7},"html":"<h2 id=\"定义\"><a href=\"#%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89\" aria-label=\"定义 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>定义</h2>\n<p>提示信息 Tooltip，指当鼠标悬停在图表上或者手指点按移动设备的某个数据点时，<strong>以交互提示</strong>信息的形式展示该点的数据，比如该点的值，数据单位等。</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"何时使用\"><a href=\"#%E4%BD%95%E6%97%B6%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8\" aria-label=\"何时使用 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>何时使用</h2>\n<p>当你希望数据可视化作品对用户的操作有所反馈时，提示信息 Tooltip 就可以发挥作用。<br />例如：当用户悬停一个数据点时，如果仅数据点样式发生变化而没有其他任何提示，这看起来就像一个 Bug，建议同步显示提示信息 Tooltip 帮助用户深入了解数据点的详情。</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"元素\"><a href=\"#%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0\" aria-label=\"元素 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>元素</h2>\n<p>Tooltip 的基本元素包括：视觉标记图形，文本标签，数值标记等。 <br />Tooltip 的可选元素：所在的 UI 容器还可以和其他 UI 组件配合使用，完成过滤，下钻等自助分析功能。</p>\n<img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/zos/basement_prod/0677c002-9804-4d12-9d3f-744ec5d3c763.svg' width=750/>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"类型\"><a href=\"#%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B\" aria-label=\"类型 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>类型</h2>\n<p>提示信息 Tooltip 按不同的图表类型，常见有如下四种：</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>跟随显示的浮层提示</th>\n<th>与图例组合显示的提示</th>\n<th>与轴组合显示的提示</th>\n<th>图形上显示的提示</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>悬浮</td>\n<td>固定位置</td>\n<td>固定在轴上</td>\n<td>固定在图形上</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_f8c6a0/afts/img/A*jWBiQa_9An0AAAAAAAAAAABkARQnAQ' width=243/></td>\n<td><img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_f8c6a0/afts/img/A*863pQ7Uw3y8AAAAAAAAAAABkARQnAQ' width=750/></td>\n<td>[<img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_f8c6a0/afts/img/A*DB8JTaxMB3sAAAAAAAAAAABkARQnAQ' width=292/></td>\n<td><img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_f8c6a0/afts/img/A*qjY2Sp_5kCwAAAAAAAAAAABkARQnAQ' width=350/></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3 id=\"跟随显示的浮层提示\"><a href=\"#%E8%B7%9F%E9%9A%8F%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E7%9A%84%E6%B5%AE%E5%B1%82%E6%8F%90%E7%A4%BA\" aria-label=\"跟随显示的浮层提示 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>跟随显示的浮层提示</h3>\n<img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_f8c6a0/afts/img/A*I-40QY9l0qsAAAAAAAAAAABkARQnAQ' width=750/>\n<p><strong>适合设备：</strong>PC 端<br /><strong>出现位置：</strong>悬浮即触发显示，跟随鼠标移动<br /><strong>适合图表类型：</strong>全部图表</p>\n<h3 id=\"与图例组合显示的提示\"><a href=\"#%E4%B8%8E%E5%9B%BE%E4%BE%8B%E7%BB%84%E5%90%88%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E7%9A%84%E6%8F%90%E7%A4%BA\" aria-label=\"与图例组合显示的提示 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>与图例组合显示的提示</h3>\n<img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_f8c6a0/afts/img/A*YzfWTYhikzYAAAAAAAAAAABkARQnAQ' width=750/>\n<p><strong>适合设备：</strong>常用于移动端，PC 端也适用<br /><strong>出现位置：</strong>图表上方<br /><strong>适合图表类型：</strong>全部图表</p>\n<h3 id=\"与轴组合显示的提示\"><a href=\"#%E4%B8%8E%E8%BD%B4%E7%BB%84%E5%90%88%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E7%9A%84%E6%8F%90%E7%A4%BA\" aria-label=\"与轴组合显示的提示 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>与轴组合显示的提示</h3>\n<img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_f8c6a0/afts/img/A*iiTwS5EqJ94AAAAAAAAAAABkARQnAQ' width=750/>\n<p><strong>适合设备：</strong>常用于 PC 端，移动端也可使用<br /><strong>出现位置：</strong>轴上，覆盖轴标签<br /><strong>适合图表类型：</strong>散点图、气泡图等迪卡尔坐标系图表</p>\n<h3 id=\"图形上显示的提示\"><a href=\"#%E5%9B%BE%E5%BD%A2%E4%B8%8A%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E7%9A%84%E6%8F%90%E7%A4%BA\"